{"tid":2080474,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我真係好想識朋友","createTime":"2020-06-26T12:28:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T02:54:59.000Z","uid":249170,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4900718d2e5f1f0baee811bc28a82bf3f2d0c104","tid":2080474,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:28:38.000Z","msg":"每次識親d男仔都會鐘意我，追我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次單獨食完飯都會捉住我隻手表白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同佢講清楚我地只係朋友關係<br />\n又會同我反面<br />\n<br />\n仲要同其他男仔朋友 fd小小都比人唱我收兵<br />\n搞到d男仔遠尻離我<br />\n我屌你老母個臭西<br />\n<br />\n其實我係真心當你地好朋友，你地個個都係好人，好快就會有正姻緣，只不過果個一定唔係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係連識個朋友都唔撚得，做人真係好大壓力<br />\n呢個世界究撚柒竟有冇純友誼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"623e2dd19e7c2edbb71124384640229c8c69d01d","tid":2080474,"uid":326758,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:30:39.000Z","msg":"我都好想識朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />識親啲人都會唔鍾意我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又會同我反面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bd823ba809ee50ae8f86d51822b855ea4a65202","tid":2080474,"uid":265217,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:31:36.000Z","msg":"樓主基？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"593638114965b8fcc15ac149c7303c2fae8a2077","tid":2080474,"uid":202125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:35:33.000Z","msg":"明呀 樓主 啲人每次見完我就話要下場落去飲酒 都唔知想做啲咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb99ce91c525724c34d6ecce194b8cf15fc120f7","tid":2080